embeds.title: Personal Pronoun Roles
embeds.description:
It isn't always easy to remember how to address someone respectfully.  These roles allow our users to let others know their personal pronouns.

To assign yourself a role, react by clicking on the relevant emoji below.

:blue_circle: <@&925846791142928475>
